you have to put in a coin.

760
01:06:42,264 --> 01:06:43,731
Ting!

761
01:06:51,474 --> 01:06:55,467
We never appreciate the good moments
till they're over.

762
01:06:55,578 --> 01:06:57,671
Maybe that's why
they're good moments.

763
01:06:57,747 --> 01:07:00,978
- We don't stop to think about them.
- Perhaps.

764
01:07:01,050 --> 01:07:02,984
What happened to Pelayo?

765
01:07:03,052 --> 01:07:05,646
- What's up?
- Hang on a minute.

766
01:07:06,522 --> 01:07:08,456
- That's it.
- About time.

767
01:07:08,524 --> 01:07:11,925
- Want anything else?
- No, thanks.

768
01:07:15,731 --> 01:07:17,631
How's things, Pelayo?

769
01:07:17,733 --> 01:07:19,325
Fine.

770
01:07:19,468 --> 01:07:21,629
How's things, Pelayo?

771
01:07:22,738 --> 01:07:24,205
Fine.

772
01:07:24,340 --> 01:07:26,604
Yeah.

773
01:07:28,310 --> 01:07:30,642
I'm actually not as fucked up
as I look.

774
01:07:30,746 --> 01:07:33,510
I'm used to you always winning,
you bastard.

775
01:07:33,582 --> 01:07:36,574
- And Sofia isn't that great.
- You said she was ideal.

776
01:07:36,685 --> 01:07:38,380
