- No, what?

832
01:13:50,492 --> 01:13:54,724
Well, yes, but that's another girl.
I know the real Sofia.

833
01:13:54,863 --> 01:13:57,127
Then tell me where she is.

834
01:13:58,400 --> 01:14:01,927
