838
01:14:14,016 --> 01:14:16,211
She was in my house
supplanting my girlfriend!

839
01:14:16,318 --> 01:14:20,379
I don't know why,
but she wouldn't press charges.

840
01:14:21,390 --> 01:14:24,325
Fucking great!
So now she's the victim!

841
01:14:24,426 --> 01:14:26,792
Tell me.
Are you on drugs?

842
01:14:26,862 --> 01:14:30,457
- God!
- You were under psychiatric care.

843
01:14:30,566 --> 01:14:33,467
My face was destroyed
in a car crash she caused!

844
01:14:33,535 --> 01:14:35,264
Your face looks fine.

845
01:14:35,370 --> 01:14:37,201
Because--

846
01:14:37,306 --> 01:14:40,173
It doesn't matter.
I've got nothing more to say.

847
01:14:40,242 --> 01:14:41,834
Young man.

848
01:14:41,910 --> 01:14:45,038
I'd advise you to see a psychiatrist.

849
01:14:52,654 --> 01:14:54,178
Are you an idiot?

850
01:14:54,289 --> 01:14:56,780
- What the fuck is this?
- What do you mean?

851
01:14:56,925 --> 01:15:01,362
Ifyou wanted to fuck her up,
there are other ways to do it!

852
01:15:02,531 --> 01:15:05,432
- Keep away from Sofia!
- It isn't Sofia. It's Nuria!

853
01:15:05,534 --> 01:15:06,831
Nuria's dead!

854
01:15:06,902 --> 01:15:09,962
Calm down, oryou'll be sleeping
