856
01:15:12,407 --> 01:15:15,865
I don't know what the cops told you,
but Nuria is alive!

857
01:15:15,978 --> 01:15:18,037
The cops didn't tell me,
Sofia did.

858
01:15:18,146 --> 01:15:20,671
Listen, you spoke to her by phone,
didn't you?

859
01:15:20,782 --> 01:15:23,182
- Let go!
- It wasn't Sofia.

860
01:15:23,252 --> 01:15:26,483
Nuria can imitate her voice.
She took her ID, her apartment.

861
01:15:26,555 --> 01:15:30,685
It wasn't over the phone.
I've just dropped her home.

862
01:15:30,826 --> 01:15:32,726
She looked like this.

863
01:15:39,434 --> 01:15:41,902
Nice photo, isn't it?

864
01:15:42,004 --> 01:15:43,995
