865
01:15:44,106 --> 01:15:47,234
But that's--
Is this a joke or what?

866
01:15:47,309 --> 01:15:49,174
You're crazy, man.

867
01:15:50,445 --> 01:15:53,243
I'm crazy? I'm crazy?

868
01:15:54,950 --> 01:15:58,215
You're the ones who are mad!
You're all mad!

869
01:15:58,287 --> 01:16:00,187
Let go of me!

870
01:16:01,390 --> 01:16:03,290
God, what's happening?

871
01:16:04,393 --> 01:16:06,293
It's my partners, right?

872
01:16:06,428 --> 01:16:08,623
They've paid you.
This is a plot!

873
01:16:08,764 --> 01:16:12,666
Look at yourself. You haven't
been right since the accident.

874
01:16:14,036 --> 01:16:15,503
Fuckyou!

875
01:16:17,773 --> 01:16:19,400
Are you saying--

876
01:16:19,508 --> 01:16:23,706
Are you saying this is the girl
you ran after the other night?

877
01:16:23,779 --> 01:16:26,077
- Is this your ideal girl?
- Yes!

878
01:16:27,616 --> 01:16:29,481
And you took her.

879
01:16:37,759 --> 01:16:39,784
You need a psychiatrist!

880
01:16:47,169 --> 01:16:48,636
Problems?

881
01:16:50,238 --> 01:16:52,138
I'm in no mood, so just--

882
01:16:52,240 --> 01:16:54,800
There's an explanation for all this.

883
01:16:54,876 --> 01:16:56,309
Cesar.

884
01:16:59,348 --> 01:17:00,713
Who are you?

885
01:17:00,782 --> 01:17:03,649
- You've seen me on TV.
- What do you want?

886
01:17:05,454 --> 01:17:07,718
I'm here to help you.

887
01:17:07,789 --> 01:17:11,418
First of all, it's very important
that you calm down.

888
01:17:11,560 --> 01:17:12,754
Calm down?

889
01:17:12,894 --> 01:17:16,386
You must overcome your fears
and regain control.

890
01:17:16,498 --> 01:17:19,467
What control do you mean?
I'm fine.

891
01:17:19,534 --> 01:17:21,263
Who says you aren't?

892
01:17:21,336 --> 01:17:24,066
They do. All of them.

893
01:17:24,172 --> 01:17:26,231
They think I'm mad.

894
01:17:26,341 --> 01:17:28,309
No, of course you're not mad.

895
01:17:28,377 --> 01:17:32,973
But what if I told you
you were dreaming?

896
01:17:37,686 --> 01:17:39,153
No, no, no.

897
01:17:39,221 --> 01:17:41,086
Why not?

898
01:17:41,189 --> 01:17:44,647
- I know what's real, and this is real.
- How do you know?

899
01:17:44,793 --> 01:17:47,318
You discoveryour dreams
when you wake.

900
01:17:47,462 --> 01:17:49,157
I just know.

901
01:17:49,297 --> 01:17:52,926
- My dreams are much simpler than this.
- No dream is simple.

902
01:17:53,068 --> 01:17:55,866
Look at those people.

903
01:17:55,971 --> 01:17:59,236
