about their own business.

904
01:17:59,341 --> 01:18:01,673
Completely unaware ofyou.

905
01:18:01,777 --> 01:18:05,770
And yet, they could be there
because you wanted it.

906
01:18:05,847 --> 01:18:10,648
What's more, you could have them
at your complete service...

907
01:18:10,752 --> 01:18:12,913
or have them destroy you.

908
01:18:13,021 --> 01:18:15,148
I want them to be quiet.

909
01:18:15,257 --> 01:18:17,157
And you, too.

910
01:18:31,239 --> 01:18:33,139
See?

911
01:18:44,252 --> 01:18:46,152
What's going on here?

912
01:18:49,958 --> 01:18:52,051
Someone tell me the fucking truth!

913
01:18:52,160 --> 01:18:55,926
The truth?
Maybe you couldn't take it.

914
01:18:59,468 --> 01:19:03,131
It had to be a setup,
a big joke to drive me crazy.

915
01:19:03,238 --> 01:19:05,900
They all knew. Nuria, Pelayo,
the police, the guy at the bar.

916
01:19:06,007 --> 01:19:08,134
- Who was he?
- I don't know.

917
01:19:08,243 --> 01:19:10,643
You said you saw him on TV.
On what program?

918
01:19:10,746 --> 01:19:12,270
I don't know!

919
01:19:13,415 --> 01:19:16,680
I don't know. One that talked
about freezing the dead.

920
01:19:16,752 --> 01:19:19,516
- Freezing the dead?
- Cryonization.

921
01:19:19,588 --> 01:19:21,715
Like they did to Walt Disney.

922
01:19:26,962 --> 01:19:29,863
Maybe I can help you remember.

923
01:19:29,931 --> 01:19:31,660
Is that a threat?

924
01:19:35,303 --> 01:19:36,895
Lie down.

925
01:19:42,377 --> 01:19:43,776
What's that?

926
01:19:43,879 --> 01:19:45,346
A syringe.

927
01:19:48,650 --> 01:19:50,277
Relax.

928
01:19:50,352 --> 01:19:51,979
My arm's stinging.

929
01:19:52,087 --> 01:19:54,578
It's a tranquilizer.

930
01:19:54,656 --> 01:19:56,351
What for?

931
01:20:05,367 --> 01:20:07,835
These things are all bullshit.

932
01:20:07,903 --> 01:20:11,839
Ifyou'd trusted psychiatrists more,
you mightn't be here now.

933
01:20:14,276 --> 01:20:17,973
That finger,
it's making me nervous.

934
01:20:18,046 --> 01:20:20,014
You needn't be afraid.

935
01:20:20,081 --> 01:20:22,709
- I'm not afraid.
- Stop talking and concentrate.

936
01:20:22,818 --> 01:20:25,013
Come on.

937
01:20:25,086 --> 01:20:26,519
Fuck.

938
01:20:28,256 --> 01:20:29,848
I feel dizzy.

939
01:20:29,958 --> 01:20:31,425
Good-bye, Cesar.

940
01:20:35,864 --> 01:20:39,561
Very good. Now let's see
ifyou can tell me about that dream.

941
01:20:41,803 --> 01:20:45,068
- In my dream, it isn't raining.
- The office dream.

942
01:20:45,173 --> 01:20:46,231
Eli.

943
01:20:46,341 --> 01:20:48,741
That's it. I want you
to tell me who Eli is.

944
01:20:48,810 --> 01:20:51,438
- A secretary.
- Eli is a secretary?

945
01:20:51,546 --> 01:20:54,276
She tells me to go in.
They're expecting me.

946
01:20:54,382 --> 01:20:56,247
Who 's expecting you?

947
01:20:57,686 --> 01:21:00,621
- The Frenchman from the TV.
- Sit down, please.

948
01:21:00,722 --> 01:21:02,849
It's a contract.

949
01:21:02,924 --> 01:21:04,915
- Eli--
- Cesar, who is Eli?

950
01:21:07,062 --> 01:21:10,190
You won 't regret it.
Sign.

951
01:21:10,332 --> 01:21:14,200
- What are you signing?
- Eli will see to everything.

952
01:21:14,269 --> 01:21:16,829
What have you signed?

953
01:21:20,775 --> 01:21:22,174
What's wrong?

954
01:21:22,277 --> 01:21:24,177
What's wrong, Cesar?

955
01:21:24,279 --> 01:21:26,179
Why are you crying?

956
01:21:26,281 --> 01:21:29,182
- I'm going to die.
- You're not going to die.

957
01:21:31,219 --> 01:21:33,551
- I don 't know how many.
- How many what?

958
01:21:33,622 --> 01:21:36,750
- Pills.
- You took pills?

959
01:21:36,858 --> 01:21:40,350
- How many should I take?
- Pills to feel better?

960
01:21:40,495 --> 01:21:42,019
I don 't want to.

961
01:21:42,130 --> 01:21:45,190
When I count to three,
you'll wake up. One. Two.

962
01:21:50,405 --> 01:21:53,636
I thought that, up to now,
you'd told me the truth.

963
01:21:55,277 --> 01:21:57,177
What do you mean?

964
01:21:57,279 --> 01:21:59,179
You said you took nothing.

965
01:22:00,115 --> 01:22:02,583
Cesar, I'll ask you
for the last time.

966
01:22:02,684 --> 01:22:05,585
- Did you take drugs?
- Fuck! Why does everyone--

967
01:22:05,654 --> 01:22:08,350
